Events.Text: Hi, Can I have your name please?
No, i would like to know about the Shadyside Inn near the east, and also the rating is important

You just remember from a previous visit that the East of town is typically very noisy. Make sure to check whether there is a Shadyside Inn in the North part of town and note down its rating. [instruction 1 of 6]
Alright, Can I have a name for the hotel please?

Scenario.UserTask: Search for Shadyside Inn near the East part of town and note its rating. Follow the instructions on the left for now.
Scenario.WizardTask: Help the user find a specific hotel.
